	<dl>
	<dt>The Anti-Social Behaviour Orders (ASBO...</dt>
	<dd><p>The Anti-Social Behaviour Orders (ASBO's) have gone some way to giving power to a community to comabat a whole number of nuisances. When are we going to get to the root problem of Anti-Social behaviour? Discipline. Teachers, Fire Brigade, Police Officers..the list goes on. Children no longer respect anyone...not even their parents.</p>
	<small>
	written 12th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/722">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=722">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

